<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>soi24 | Retro-Future Experiments</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Shippori+Mincho:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+Thai:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Press+Start+2P&family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700;900&family=Comfortaa:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Quicksand:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=typography"></script>
  <style>
    /* ヘルタースケルター風カラーパレット */
    :root {
      --pink-neon: #ff6ec7;
      --pink-pastel: #ffb3d9;
      --lavender: #c8a2d8;
      --mint: #a8e6cf;
      --yellow: #ffd93d;
      --cyan: #6ecff6;
      --magenta: #ff1493;
      --purple: #ba55d3;
      --bg-dark: #0a0a12;
      --bg-glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    }
    
    /* ベースフォント: 丸みを帯びた洗練されたサンセリフ */
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', 'Outfit', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.15), transparent 50%),
                  radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom right, rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.12), transparent 50%),
                  radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.1), transparent 50%),
                  linear-gradient(135deg, #0a0a12 0%, #1a0f2e 50%, #0a0a12 100%);
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }
    
    /* 明朝体: エレガントな要素に */
    .font-mincho {
      font-family: 'Shippori Mincho', 'Noto Serif JP', 'Hiragino Mincho ProN', 'Yu Mincho', serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    /* 丸みを帯びたサンセリフ: UI要素や本文に */
    .font-gothic {
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', 'Outfit', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    
    /* モノスペース: ラベルやタグ、数字に */
    .font-mono {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Consolas', monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      font-weight: 400;
    }
    
    /* 見出しのスタイリング: 丸みを帯びたポップなフォント */
    h1, h2, h3 {
      font-family: 'Comfortaa', 'Quicksand', 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }
    
    h2 {
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    
    h3 {
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }
    
    /* 本文は丸みを帯びたサンセリフで */
    p {
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-weight: 300;
    }
    
    /* ナビゲーションは洗練されたサンセリフで */
    nav {
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    }
    
    /* ラベルやタグはモノスペースで */
    .label, .tag {
      font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    }
    
    /* ボタンは丸みを帯びたサンセリフで */
    button, a.btn-glow {
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }
    .neon-pulse::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: -20%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.15), rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.1), rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.08), transparent 60%);
      filter: blur(60px);
      animation: pulse 12s ease-in-out infinite;
      opacity: 0.5;
      pointer-events: none;
      will-change: transform, opacity;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    .project-card::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.3), rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.25), rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.2), rgba(255, 217, 61, 0.15));
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 400ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
      pointer-events: none;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
    }
    .project-card:hover::after {
      opacity: 0.3;
    }
    .btn-glow {
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5), 
                  0 0 50px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.3),
                  0 4px 20px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.2);
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    }
    .btn-glow:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6), 
                  0 0 60px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.4),
                  0 6px 25px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.25);
      transform: translateY(-2px) translateZ(0);
    }
    .fade-ready {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px) translateZ(0);
      will-change: opacity, transform;
    }
    .fade-visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0) translateZ(0);
      transition: opacity 700ms ease-out, transform 700ms ease-out;
      will-change: auto;
    }
    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% {
        transform: scale(0.98) translateZ(0);
        opacity: 0.5;
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1.02) translateZ(0);
        opacity: 0.7;
      }
    }
    
    /* レトロフューチャー要素 */
    
    /* ソフトなスキャンライン効果 */
    .scanlines {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        0deg,
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.02),
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.02) 1px,
        transparent 1px,
        transparent 4px
      );
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1000;
      opacity: 0.3;
      will-change: auto;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    /* ポップなドットパターン */
    .pixel-pattern {
      background-image: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.08) 1px, transparent 0);
      background-size: 30px 30px;
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
      opacity: 0.4;
      will-change: auto;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    /* ポップなネオンサイン */
    .neon-blink {
      animation: neonBlink 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      will-change: opacity, text-shadow;
    }
    
    @keyframes neonBlink {
      0%, 100% {
        opacity: 1;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6), 
                     0 0 40px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.4), 
                     0 0 60px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.2);
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 0.85;
        text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.4), 
                     0 0 30px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.3);
      }
    }
    
    .neon-blink-cyan {
      animation: neonBlinkCyan 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
      will-change: opacity, text-shadow;
    }
    
    @keyframes neonBlinkCyan {
      0%, 100% {
        opacity: 1;
        text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.6), 
                     0 0 40px rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.4), 
                     0 0 60px rgba(110, 207, 246, 0.2);
      }
      50% {
        opacity: 0.8;
        text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.4), 
                     0 0 30px rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.3);
      }
    }
    
    /* ソフトなグリッド */
    .mechanical-grid {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: 
        linear-gradient(rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 80px 80px, 80px 80px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.3;
      will-change: auto;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    /* ドット絵風の装飾要素 */
    .pixel-decoration {
      image-rendering: pixelated;
      image-rendering: -moz-crisp-edges;
      image-rendering: crisp-edges;
    }
    
    /* ポップなボーダー */
    .retro-border {
      border: 2px solid;
      border-image: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6), rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.5), rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.4)) 1;
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 20px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.4),
        inset 0 0 20px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.2);
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    /* ポップな点滅ドット */
    .blinking-dot {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 110, 199, 1), rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6));
      border-radius: 50%;
      animation: dotBlink 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
      box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.7),
                  0 0 24px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.3);
      will-change: transform, opacity;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    @keyframes dotBlink {
      0%, 100% { 
        opacity: 1; 
        transform: scale(1) translateZ(0);
      }
      50% { 
        opacity: 0.5; 
        transform: scale(0.85) translateZ(0);
      }
    }
    
    /* グラスモーフィズム風のフレーム */
    .arcade-frame {
      position: relative;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      will-change: transform;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    .arcade-frame::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -3px;
      left: -3px;
      right: -3px;
      bottom: -3px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.4), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.3), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.2));
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      z-index: -1;
      animation: frameGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      opacity: 0.6;
      filter: blur(6px);
      will-change: transform, opacity;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    .arcade-frame::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.3), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.25), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.2)) padding-box,
        linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.5), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.4)) border-box;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }
    
    @keyframes frameGlow {
      0%, 100% { 
        opacity: 0.6; 
        transform: scale(1) translateZ(0);
      }
      50% { 
        opacity: 0.9; 
        transform: scale(1.01) translateZ(0);
      }
    }
    
    /* ポップなレトロフューチャー要素 */
    
    /* 見出しスタイル（丸みを帯びたポップなフォント） */
    .comic-text {
      font-family: 'Comfortaa', 'Quicksand', 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      line-height: 1.4;
      overflow-wrap: break-word;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 1), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 1), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 1));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    
    /* ポップな装飾バッジ */
    .steampunk-badge {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.2), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.15), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.1));
      border: 2px solid rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5);
      border-radius: 2rem;
      box-shadow: 
        inset 0 0 15px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.2),
        0 0 20px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.3),
        0 4px 15px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.2);
      font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      font-weight: 500;
      will-change: transform;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    .steampunk-badge::before {
      content: '✦';
      position: absolute;
      left: -12px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.8);
      animation: sparkle 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    
    @keyframes sparkle {
      0%, 100% { 
        opacity: 1; 
        transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1) rotate(0deg) translateZ(0);
      }
      50% { 
        opacity: 0.7; 
        transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.15) rotate(180deg) translateZ(0);
      }
    }
    
    /* ポップな装飾 */
    .japanese-steampunk {
      position: relative;
    }
    
    .japanese-steampunk::before {
      content: '✨';
      position: absolute;
      top: -25px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      font-size: 2rem;
      opacity: 0.3;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    
    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0) translateZ(0); }
      50% { transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-8px) translateZ(0); }
    }
    
    /* ポップな吹き出し */
    .comic-bubble {
      position: relative;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.8rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.15), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.12), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.1));
      border: 3px solid rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6);
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 30px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.4),
        inset 0 0 30px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.15);
      will-change: transform;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    .comic-bubble::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -18px;
      left: 40px;
      width: 0;
      height: 0;
      border-left: 18px solid transparent;
      border-right: 18px solid transparent;
      border-top: 18px solid rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 15px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5));
    }
    
    /* ソフトなパターン */
    .mechanical-pattern {
      background-image: 
        repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, 
          transparent, 
          transparent 20px, 
          rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.03) 20px, 
          rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.03) 40px);
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0.25;
      will-change: auto;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    /* ジャパニーズテキスト装飾 */
    .japanese-accent {
      position: relative;
      display: inline-block;
    }
    
    .japanese-accent::before {
      content: '【';
      color: rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.7);
      margin-right: 0.2em;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5);
    }
    
    .japanese-accent::after {
      content: '】';
      color: rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.7);
      margin-left: 0.2em;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5);
    }
    
    /* ポップなパネル */
    .comic-panel {
      position: relative;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.1), 
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.08), 
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.06));
      border: 3px solid rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6);
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 
        0 0 40px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.4),
        inset 0 0 40px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.2);
      will-change: transform;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    .comic-panel::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -4px;
      left: -4px;
      right: -4px;
      bottom: -4px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
        rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5),
        rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.4),
        rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.3));
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      z-index: -1;
      animation: panelGlow 5s ease-in-out infinite;
      filter: blur(8px);
      will-change: transform, opacity;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    
    @keyframes panelGlow {
      0%, 100% { 
        opacity: 0.6; 
        transform: scale(1) translateZ(0);
      }
      50% { 
        opacity: 0.9; 
        transform: scale(1.01) translateZ(0);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="text-white antialiased">
  <!-- レトロフューチャー背景要素 -->
  <div class="mechanical-grid"></div>
  <div class="scanlines"></div>
  
  <div class="relative min-h-screen overflow-hidden" style="contain: layout style paint;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 neon-pulse"></div>
    <div class="pixel-pattern"></div>
    <div class="mechanical-pattern"></div>
    <header class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10 flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <span class="font-gothic text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] font-medium neon-blink" style="color: #ff6ec7;">soi24</span>
        <span class="font-gothic text-sm font-light tracking-wide" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);">Retro-Future Studio</span>
      </div>
      <nav class="font-gothic flex gap-6 text-sm font-medium">
        <a href="#projects" class="transition-all duration-300 ease-out tracking-wide" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);" onmouseover="this.style.color='#ff6ec7'; this.style.textShadow='0 0 15px rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.6)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)'; this.style.textShadow='none'">Projects</a>
        <a href="#about" class="transition-all duration-300 ease-out tracking-wide" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);" onmouseover="this.style.color='#c8a2d8'; this.style.textShadow='0 0 15px rgba(200, 162, 216, 0.6)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)'; this.style.textShadow='none'">About</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="transition-all duration-300 ease-out tracking-wide" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);" onmouseover="this.style.color='#a8e6cf'; this.style.textShadow='0 0 15px rgba(168, 230, 207, 0.6)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)'; this.style.textShadow='none'">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="relative z-10 px-6">
      <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto pt-20 pb-24 text-center" id="hero">
        <div class="fade-ready" data-observe>
          <p class="font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.5em] uppercase mb-6 font-medium neon-blink" style="color: #ff6ec7;">soi24.com<span class="blinking-dot ml-2"></span></p>
          <h1 class="mb-8">
            <span class="block mb-3 comic-text" style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);">Retro Future Studio</span>
            <span class="block mt-2 neon-blink-cyan" style="font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); font-weight: 500; font-family: 'Poppins', 'Quicksand', sans-serif; color: #a8e6cf;">Small Web Tools, AI-Assisted Development</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg tracking-wide mt-8" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">
            一瞬のひらめきが息づきはじめる。AI と紡いで、そっとカタチへ。
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="projects" class="max-w-6xl mx-auto py-20">
        <div class="fade-ready" data-observe>
          <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="japanese-steampunk">
              <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.5em] mb-4 font-medium steampunk-badge" style="color: #ff6ec7;">Projects</p>
              <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl comic-text">Vibe Coding Arsenal</h2>
            </div>
            <p class="md:max-w-xl leading-relaxed text-sm tracking-wide" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);">
              本サイトでは、AI と共に構築したプロトタイプやツール類を公開している。開発プロセスは明確性、機能的な十分性、不要な複雑化の回避を重視する。The development process emphasizes clarity, functional sufficiency, and avoidance of unnecessary complexity.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <article class="project-card arcade-frame relative rounded-2xl p-6 transition-all duration-300 ease-out" style="border: 1px solid rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.2); background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03); box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.5)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255, 110, 199, 0.2)'">
